#

Grilled Lemon Herb Chicken with Garlic Mashed Potatoes

45 min
$15
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main CourseSide Dish

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodGrilledChickenPotatoes

Description

Juicy grilled chicken infused with zesty lemon and herbs, served alongside creamy garlic mashed potatoes for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • chicken breasts: 4 pieces
  • lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic (minced): 4 cloves
  • dried oregano: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • potatoes (peeled and cubed): 2 pounds
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • milk: 1/2 cup
  • parsley (chopped, for garnish): 2 tablespoons
